==English==
===Noun===
'''lapse'''
# a [[temporary]] [[failure]]; a [[slip]]
# a [[decline]] or [[fall]] in [[standard]]s
# a [[pause]] in [[continuity]]
# an [[interval]] of [[time]] between [[event]]s
# a [[termination]] of a [[right]] etc, through [[disuse]] or [[neglect]]
===Verb===
'''to lapse''' (''transitive'')
# to allow something to lapse
'''to lapse''' (''intransitive'')
# to suffer a lapse